# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| Latest MC version   | :white_check_mark: |
| 1.8 >= | :white_check_mark: |
| < 1.8  | :x:                |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

Please contact me through [Discord](https://discord.gg/QFTjs3g) if you wish to report some vulnerability
